data.title: Well, It Ain't Toothpaste!
data.text:
Play Aozora: Ancient Abyss Now for FREE!

We got a special one today! Longtime community member Iffy/CelestialBlade is making her gamedev debut, and you can hop on over to itch.io and grab it for free right now!

Join skyfaring adventurer and ninja-in-training Lena on her latest journey to solve the mysteries of the ancient Nascian people--a lost, high-tech society and the last known inhabitants of the ruined surface beneath the sea of clouds.

Enjoy a short-form RPG with lots of challenging meaty battles and cute maps to explore!

GO NOW!

Polly

Fear not, the summer heat hasn't completely melted all of us yet...at least we hope Garden's still doing okay over there. We Like Bad Music Only Show and Tell returns to discuss Garden's pick, Carole King's 1971 classic, Tapestry.

Polly

Life gets busy sometimes, but that doesn't mean your pals at We Like Bad Music Only won't be back to hit you with more music takes that you can certainly hear on the internet!

The Show and Tell project continues, this time with Garden having something to show the class! We give an introduction to that here as well as talk about 90's snacks and sodas for some reason!

Polly

Run Time: 1:41:47 / File Size: 46.5MB

Don't worry, we didn't forget about this one. Life just kinda...explodes sometimes and it takes a while to get to things, but we've finally made it back in time for Psychic_Heist to finally guide the class on a jaunty little stroll through his pick for Show & Tell, Mandy Moore's 2009 album Amanda Leigh.
